SNIPER wakes up and looks around. he sees that HELL BEAST, LIONO, 
BRIGHTBLADE, TAVATRON are still outside. he opens up his back 
compartment and searches for the right gun. he pulls out a double 
barrel rocket launcher. he aims it at HELL BEAST and fires 6 rockets 
at him. SNIPER starts to laugh.....



ZERGLING stands in the alliance wepon room serching for the right 
wepon. He finds it and smiles. It is a sword that looks like an bow 
with the handle in the middle. out of the middlecomes a double barrel 
pulse ion cannon. he places it in his tail. Then, he goes and looks 
for Zardus....
